---
// TheFix.astro
---
<section id="what-makes-us-different" class="relative py-16 px-6 text-base-content">
	<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
		<div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-base-200 to-base-300"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto">
		<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-12 text-center tracking-tight">
			What Makes Our Water Heater Replacement Service Different
		</h2>
		<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">Local, Licensed, and Fully Insured</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We’re not a lead service or franchise—we're based right here in West Michigan. We handle permits, follow code, and carry full insurance so you’re protected at every step.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">Clear, Honest Pricing Up Front</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We provide straightforward quotes with no surprise fees. You'll know exactly what’s included and what your replacement will cost before we begin. If you have questions, then we’ll make a recommendation.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">Fast Turnaround, Same-Day Available</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We’re equipped to handle most standard replacements today or tomorrow. No waiting, no wondering when we’ll show up. We respect your time, your comfort, and your budget.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">Real Experience in the Mechanical Trades</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						With 25+ years in HVAC and plumbing systems, we know the details that matter — from code compliance to venting to water line safety. This isn’t a side hustle — it’s our specialty.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">No Sales Gimmicks — Just the Right Fit</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						If you know what you want, that's what we’ll do. We're not here to push you into our pretend membership club with fake time-sensitive discounts. We install the right size and type for your home, budget, and water usage — and make sure it’s built to last.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 relative">
				<div class="absolute top-9.5 left-0 w-5 h-5 bg-primary rotate-45 -translate-x-2.5 -translate-y-2.5 rounded-sm rounded-tr-none"></div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-lg font-semibold">We Respect Your Home</h3>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We get the job done quickly and are mindful you may have other things going on in the home. We clean up thoroughly, and are always careful with your property. No mess, no stress.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
